Package net.hudup.em

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EM
    EM is the most abstract interface for all expectation maximization (EM) algorithm.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEM
    AbstractEM is the most abstract class for expectation maximization (EM) algorithm.
    EMLearningEvent
    This class represents events when expectation maximization (EM) algorithm runs.
    ExponentialEM
    This abstract class model a expectation maximization (EM) algorithm for exponential family.
    GEM
    This class represents the generalized expectation maximization (GEM) algorithm.
    NewtonGEM
    This abstract class implements partially expectation maximization (EM) algorithm associated Newton-Raphson method.
